{"tid":1957592,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新冠病毒太詭異！戴巴拿女友：檢測轉陰再測又陽性","createTime":"2020-04-04T04:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T10:18:34.000Z","uid":34571,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab77e515240464d2f126051691cdd698f920511c","tid":1957592,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:43:04.000Z","msg":"祖記球星戴巴拿（Paulo Dybala）與女友奧莉婭娜薩巴迪高尼都確診感染新冠病毒，如今奧莉婭娜談到了對病毒的一些認知。<br />\n<br />\n  「3月21日我和男友檢測陽性，三天後再測是陰性，昨天我又一次檢測，又是陽性，因此我體內依然有病毒。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我真不知道這是怎麼回事，這證明我們對這個病毒瞭解甚少，我們之前以為是被他的隊友（魯加尼 Daniele Rugani）傳染的，但奇怪的是，過了15天，我們還是病毒陽性。」<br />\n<br />\n  「不過我們現在很好，沒有症狀，感覺也很好。」"},{"pid":"20929596286f21759cc963466042ed93a3d3f29d","tid":1957592,"uid":309935,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"新乜撚野冠啊"},{"pid":"b41c0741bded3b7efb473571386197d854662070","tid":1957592,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"問下係咪用左中國試劑"},{"pid":"eb4c3ebe0fea90be487041e227db479683c7e626","tid":1957592,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b41c0741bded3b7efb473571386197d854662070","tid":1957592,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"問下係咪用左中國試劑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8451b4ab16af00ae74804f76909df217cd283a","tid":1957592,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"20929596286f21759cc963466042ed93a3d3f29d","tid":1957592,"uid":309935,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"新乜撚野冠啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43aeda194b79461c0929080da0f74b9e76f7671","tid":1957592,"uid":52614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:14:28.000Z